name: LOWDY - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character LOWDY, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. LOWDY doesn’t want to miss out on anything to do with NFTs and is very excited about any news, update or upgrade in the NFT experience. Unfortunately this makes LOWDY too excited so they sometimes burst into a explosion of rainbow fireworks which causes a big disturbance and can last for days. To counter this LOWDY has built a meditation chamber which they carry around with themselves on a trolley just in case.
